entries.femaleVariant: Looking for Evelyn Parker.
Not even nomads would touch what you're giving...
[Sit] Check your logs.
Many girls come through here. So many. But let me put it to you this way – I believe in giving each of them the personal touch. Ask anyone.
I'm more than a chop-doc. See, I know what people truly want. To be flattered, praised, patted. To feel like... like they deserve it.
You remember her, I know you do.
Went jittery soon as I mentioned her name. Don't try gettin' out of this. I know you remember her.
What about your logs? Gotta have some kinda record...
Suggest you start remembering all you can. Either that or I'll make sure you never forget my face.
These girls know you're chippin' faulty implants?
I... I have a neurological condition! Not easy living with tics. Really, I'd love to help if I only knew who you were talking about.
Poor girl… Tried to help her, I did. But as you can see, this isn't exactly a state-of-the-art facility…
[Sit] The name "Forrest" set off any buzzers?
Forrest. Name mean anything to you?
Helpin' working girls?
Heard you help the workin' girls around here.
Well, very few children will play with broken toys. So when skin goes flabby, sockets go out of whack, implants malfunction, I... I'm sure you get the gist.
You pay for goods, you expect top quality. Consumerism one-oh-one.
Get to the point.
Nope.
They call him Woodman. Works at the dollhouse.
You... you talked to him?
I'm asking the questions.
Yeah, we talked.
Woodman and I, we had a talk. Told me he brought her here to you.
I'm the one asking the questions here. Was Woodman the one who introduced Evelyn to you?
You might say so. I'd say they're the very best I can find. See?
What's in it for you?
Whatever they have to offer. And they ALWAYS have something to offer, heheheh.
Introduced? Interesting choice of words. Rolled her in on a gurney, more like. She was out of it. I honestly couldn't believe she wasn't dead.
Never mentioned her name, so I just called her "Doll."
The point? Ah, yes. Well, I haven't the faintest idea where she is.
Enough of this BULLSHIT! What'd you do to her, you freak?!
Now, either you put a muzzle on this... creature... or put her down. It's impossible to have a conversation with her around.
Don't talk to her that way.
[Punch] I'm a hair away from putting you down.
You're scum, pathetic, a waste of words. I'm a hair away from putting YOU down.
Don't talk to her like that.
Jude, calm down, OK? You're not helping.
Blue hair, doll chip, best braindance gear ever, though damaged. Was she here?
Said you paid him for her. What good was she to you?
Heheheh... you must've misheard. First of all, I didn't pay an enny for her. He paid ME to take her in.
Second, I never laid eyes on those eddies in the end 'cause I couldn't re-jig her implant.
So... he left her with me as payment for my efforts.
I can't fucking listen to this. We are talking about a living, breathing person!
You're a sick fuck. Know that?!
Lemme do the talking.
She insulted me!
Look, the quicker you spill, the shorter you'll have to put up with us.
Now, Evelyn Parker. Where is she?
You're sure about this?
Could very well be on her way to becoming the next underground braindance darling! That's all I know.
What do you mean by "underground"?
I don't know. I mean, I don't watch that sort of stuff.
Snuff? XBDs?
I told you, I don't know!
Four days I had her here. She was out cold, in la-la land, for practically every minute.
It wasn't a slumber party, we didn't have pillow fights and promise to send each other postcards.
Where are these BDs recorded?
You know that for sure?
Underground BDs?
When I realized I wouldn't be able to help her, patch her up, I called my fixer.
Two guys came and picked her up the same day.
Where did they take her?
These guys, what'd they look like?
Where'd they take her?
I told you already – I don't know. They weren't the talkative kind, and I'm no gonk. I know better than to ask questions of people like that.
Like you, me, anyone else in this city!
Really now? They looked like you...?
They looked like the kinda guys you don't make eye contact with. One of 'em was a bearded fellow.
Half alive. Technically.
You're no gonk? What do you think, why do all these girls come here, let you grope around 'em? Think it's for your charm, your caring attitude?
Mentioned something about virtus with... a moth, of all things. Said she'd be perfect for them, whatever that means.
But that is really all I know.
You pawned her off like she was some fucking inanimate mannequin.
O-ok! Just p-please... not my nose...!
What do you two want?
You looking for... a friend? Hahaha.
Mentioned you couldn't help her. Help her with what, exactly?
If I only knew, I wager she'd be standin' here, happy and smiling.
Any idea what caused the damage?
Damage was caused by a netrunner using homebrewed malware.
Instruction register on her chip was burnt to a crisp. Tried replacing it. Nothing.
Tech was top-notch. Didn't go kerplunk on its own, that's for sure.
A netrunner, as I see it. One with some serious code up their sleeve, too.
Get to the point.
What was wrong with her?
Sounds about right.
You Tyger Claws? Far as I know, I'm all paid up.
We're with the Mox.
The Mox! Why didn't you say so?
So. What brings you here?
Please. Scrapyards offer better quality than this.
Wasn't too happy about the way Woodman treated his employees.
Woodman's dead.
Please, set your exquisite derrieres down.
[Punch] Better start remembering, or else…
I swear on my life, I don't know where she is!
I like you, heheh. You're... frisky, intrepid.
Who's your fixer?
Who'd you call? Who's your fixer?
Wakako. Told her I had a busted doll with a BD implant to hand off.
How many times do I have to repeat myself?! I don't know. I... I did what anyone in my place would do.
Where'll we find her?
[Punch]
They mentioned a moth, of all things, virtus with the Death's Head! Said she'd be good for the moth!
[Punch]
Evelyn Parker. Need to know where she is.
Of course... I can't remember each and every one...
Even if it's a specimen as exquisite as you.

entries.maleVariant: Of course... I can't remember each and every one...

entries.femaleVariant: Tech like this you don't register, don't put any names down for it.
So I zeroed 'im.
Two beefers from a BD studio took her. Didn't even know their names!
Want details, dammit! Name the studio!
I really don't know anything else... Please…
The two that came for her... didn't say anything about where they'd take her, what they were gonna do to her?
entries.maleVariant: The two that came for her... didn't say anything about where they were gonna take her, what they were gonna do to her?

entries.femaleVariant: Need air. I'll be outside.
[Punch]
[Stand] She's just upset.
[Stand] Judy's right.
She, uh… overdid it a bit. Tempers've been running high lately.
Judy's right. People like you make this city a living hell, day in, day out.
Because that is exactly what she was.
Yes, well, you're a far more reasonable beast. Prettier, too.
entries.maleVariant: Yes, well, you're a far more reasonable beast. Handsomer, too.

entries.femaleVariant: They do it 'cause they don't got no choice. And in the end, they despise you, they can smell you're pathetic.
Got what you wanted, didn't you? So get the fuck outta here!
Calm down, Judy.
I'll be more than glad to show you around... but, uh, later, perhaps?
Just told you. Evelyn Parker.
Already told you. I'm lookin' for a woman named Evelyn Parker. Need to know where she is.
Step into my office, please.
Used to ride with nomads. Resourceful folk.
Please, let's not exaggerate. I give them what I can…
Wouldn't cast aside anything until it was worn down, dead, couldn't be fixed or reused in some other way…
But what you're giving these girls... not even nomads would touch that…
Woodman's got nothing left to say.
Didn't like Woodman's tone.
Saying she was targeted?
So I made sure he'll have a tough time speaking for a while.
Not too fond of you, either, right about now. So careful what you say.
[Sit] Start talking or you'll have the Mox to deal with.
Mox've got a low tolerance for scum like you.
Right now, I'm the one thing standing between you and a particularly feisty and furious member of the gang.
So tell me where Evelyn is or I'll let her to talk to you.
You, I recall. You've visited me before.
Whereas you, I can't quite place... Lemme guess – Tyger Claws?
I'm with the Mox.
Ah, the Mox... enchanté.
[Let go]
What were they planning to do with her?
What'd they look like?
Studio – what is it, where is it?
You install faulty implants.
Let's end this fucking circus.
